ml;ppen dygnet runt.\n                                <br>\n<br>\n                                F&ouml;r att ditt mail och sms ska komma r&auml;tt m&aring;ste du anv&auml;nda den mail-adress och det mobilnummer du angav n&auml;r\n                                du bokade resan (detta ser du p&aring; \"Min resa\").\n                                Om du vill &auml;ndra dessa uppgifter g&ouml;r du det genom att besvara detta mail.\n                                <br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<b>Vill du uppleva mer p&aring; semestern?</b></td><td></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table align=\"center\" width=\"470\" style=\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff; WIDTH: 470px\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"15\" style=\"WIDTH: 15px\"></td><td align=\"left\" width=\"440\" vAlign=\"top\" style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; WIDTH: 440px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: top\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.fritidsresor.se/skyddad-sida/myholiday.aspx\"><img height=\"160\" width=\"440\" border=\"0\" src=\"https://tui-appgw.sigma.se/email/email-img/FRG_tui_440x160_utflykter_2_SV_.png\"></a></td><td width=\"15\" style=\"WIDTH: 15px\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"15\" style=\"WIDTH: 15px\"></td><td align=\"left\" width=\"440\" vAlign=\"top\" class=\"brodtext1\" style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; WIDTH: 440px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: top\">\n                        F&ouml;lj med p&aring; n&aring;gon av v&aring;ra utflykter! Redan nu kan du logga in p&aring; \"Min resa\" p&aring; fritidsresor.se och boka och betala dina utflykter. Du kan &auml;ven boka v&aring;ra utflykter via \"Min resa\" p&aring; fritidsresor.se under semestern.\n                    <br>\n<br>\n</td><td width=\"15\" style=\"WIDTH: 15px\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"15\" style=\"WIDTH: 15px\"></td><td align=\"left\" width=\"440\" vAlign=\"top\" style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; WIDTH: 440px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: top\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.fritidsresor.se/Att-resa-med-oss/Infor-resan/Hyrbil/\"><img height=\"160\" width=\"440\" src=\"https://tui-appgw.sigma.se/email/email-img/FRG_tui_440x160_panorama_hyrbil_SV.png\" border=\"0\"></a></td><td width=\"15\" style=\"WIDTH: 15px\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"15\" style=\"WIDTH: 15px\"></td><td align=\"left\" width=\"440\" vAlign=\"top\" class=\"brodtext1\" style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; WIDTH: 440px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: top\">\n                    Du kanske vill hyra bil under semestern? Boka din hyrbil genom oss s&aring; &auml;r alla praktiska detaljer ordnade\n                    innan du reser.\n                    <br>\n<br>\n</td><td width=\"15\" style=\"WIDTH: 15px\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"15\" style=\"WIDTH: 15px\"></td><td align=\"left\" width=\"440\" vAlign=\"top\" style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; WIDTH: 440px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: top\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.fritidsresor.se/resa/Grekland/Rhodos/reseberattelser/?season=sommar-2014\"><img height=\"160\" width=\"440\" src=\"https://tui-appgw.sigma.se/email/email-img/FRG_tui_440x160_insidertips_SV.png\" border=\"0\"></a></td><td width=\"15\" style=\"WIDTH: 15px\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"15\" style=\"WIDTH: 15px\"></td><td align=\"left\" width=\"440\" vAlign=\"top\" class=\"brodtext1\" style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; WIDTH: 440px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: top\">\n                    Insidertips &auml;r personliga restips fr&aring;n alla som arbetar p&aring; Fritidsresor. H&auml;r hittar du v&aring;ra b&auml;sta tips p&aring; allt fr&aring;n restauranger och sev&auml;rdheter till hemliga str&auml;nder och saker att g&ouml;ra p&aring; v&aring;ra resm&aring;l.\n                    <br>\n<br>\n</td><td width=\"15\" style=\"WIDTH: 15px\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table align=\"center\" width=\"470\" style=\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff; WIDTH: 470px\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"15\" style=\"WIDTH: 15px\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table align=\"center\" width=\"470\" style=\"BACKGROUND-COLOR: #ffffff; WIDTH: 470px\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"15\" style=\"WIDTH: 15px\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<